Over his right shoulder, he carries his cataclysmic weapon — a portable citadel tower, a massive, hollowed‑out fortress of ancient grey masonry, its windows and battlements overgrown with vines. The business end erupts in a jagged cluster of raw, glowing etheric blue crystals.

