His lower body is shorter, with a mechanical, piston‑driven peg‑leg in place of his right leg. A heavy, ornate gold‑buckled belt cinches his waist.

His posture is one of commanding, terrifying authority. He is a one‑ship armada, the phantom fleet’s admiral. A tiny vermilion label floats near the ship.

The Distant Academy: On the far right horizon, across the water, the faint, floating, lavender‑silver spires of the Magic Academy are just visible, their serene light a stark contrast to the ghostly teal of the fleet.

